Hello <@U03QEU2MF5G>

Yes this is possible but you have to require some edits. Follow the steps

Steps 1: Clone the quote theme.
Steps 2: Go to the clone quotes theme modules folder.
Steps 3: Open the line_items_table.module. below screenshot.  Edits the code here and remove the fields code that you don't need

You can also spin up a <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/platform/developer-projects-setup|developer sandbox> if you have Sales/Service Ent through the CRM Dev Tools Beta. I don't think it syncs as much as the "Standard" sandbox, but it still pulls object schemas which is pretty handy for dev.
